gs have been incorporated; and an entirely new chapter has been added—a topical presentation of the several factors influencing distribution of organisms along the shore. This edition also includes John Steinbeck's Foreword to the 1948 edition.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4aScience. 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Zoology / General.2bisacsh1 aCalvin, Jack, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertStanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000z978311070421140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362132940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503621329423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503621329/original  a978-3-11-070421-1  Stanford University Press Archive eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aGBV-deGruyter-alles